WEBVTT

00:12.200 --> 00:17.720
[pastor in Swedish] Immediately
after the tribulation of those days,

00:17.800 --> 00:20.760
the sun will be darkened,

00:20.840 --> 00:23.800
and the moon will not give its light,

00:23.880 --> 00:29.000
and the powers of the heavens
will be shaken.

00:29.080 --> 00:30.840
Then...

00:31.640 --> 00:36.800
...will appear the sign of my arrival,
which will be seen in heaven.

00:38.160 --> 00:40.040
Time has come, my friends.

00:40.120 --> 00:42.400
[all]
Hallelujah.

00:42.480 --> 00:44.360
Three.

00:44.440 --> 00:45.800
Two.

00:45.880 --> 00:47.600
One.

00:47.680 --> 00:48.960
