I was so sure.

01:27.680 --> 01:29.720
Judgment day is here.

01:29.800 --> 01:32.120
Come and get me, my Lord!

01:32.200 --> 01:34.520
He's losing it.

01:34.600 --> 01:36.040
I know.

01:36.120 --> 01:40.360
Maybe it's about time
to go home to Norway?

01:40.440 --> 01:42.440
My God.

01:42.520 --> 01:46.280
My God.

01:46.360 --> 01:48.960
[theme music playing]

02:22.160 --> 02:24.600
[in English]
Don't forget to water down the booze.

02:24.680 --> 02:27.760
Them hillbillies from FÃ¥berg
are so full of moonshine,

02:27.880 --> 02:29.800
- they can't tell the difference.
- Got it, boss.

