[in Norwegian]
What's going on in Oslo?

02:37.880 --> 02:39.960
[in English]
Ah, it's a personal matter.

02:40.040 --> 02:41.400
You sure you're ready for this?

02:41.480 --> 02:44.600
[yawning]
I was born ready, sir.

02:44.680 --> 02:46.520
Really?

02:46.600 --> 02:49.200
I was up all night
watching a moon eclipse.

02:49.280 --> 02:51.080
Fascinating stuff.

02:51.160 --> 02:53.080
A lunar eclipse?

02:53.160 --> 02:55.160
Now you're really starting to worry me.

02:55.240 --> 02:56.840
[in Norwegian]
Relax, Johnny. I'm here too.

02:56.920 --> 03:00.320
Ready to step in if my brother
is not on top of his game.

03:00.400 --> 03:02.840
That gives me
enormous comfort, my friend.

03:14.560 --> 03:16.920
[black metal music playing loudly]

03:17.000 --> 03:18.120
Hey.

03:19.840 --> 03:22.120
Uh, do you mind?

03:22.200 --> 03:24.200
- [in Norwegian] Sorry.
- [music stops]

03:24.280 --> 03:28.040
