when there's stress at work.

03:28.120 --> 03:31.480
Venom, Hellhammer, Mayhem.

03:31.560 --> 03:35.000
[in English] Sounds more like dogshit,
horseshit and mooseshit to me.

03:35.080 --> 03:36.920
[in Norwegian]
No reason to be a smart-ass.

03:37.000 --> 03:38.600
