you know.

03:38.680 --> 03:41.880
[in English]
Yeah, about that. Uh...

03:41.960 --> 03:44.680
There's something about this
that doesn't quite add up to me.

03:44.760 --> 03:47.080
[in Norwegian]
All right?

03:47.160 --> 03:50.520
[in English] The, uh, files that got lost,
they were, uh, found

03:50.600 --> 03:52.800
- in a regular safety deposit box?
- Mm-hmm.

03:52.880 --> 03:56.520
Don't you have, like, a secret
vault or some shit like that?

03:56.600 --> 03:58.760
[in Norwegian]
The bank box didn't belong to the PST.

03:58.840 --> 04:01.640
It was more of a private arrangement.

04:01.720 --> 04:03.480
Let's say it's my pension fund.

04:03.560 --> 04:06.400
[in English] So you stole my file
from your own people.

04:06.480 --> 04:10.000
[in Norwegian] You know information
about others is valuable stuff.

04:14.120 --> 04:16.960
And who exactly is this guy
we're going to meet?

04:17.040 --> 04:21.440
[Johnny in English] Let's just say he's
in a perfect place at the perfect time.

04:21.520 --> 04:24.280
[in Norwegian]
Really hungry, you.

04:24.360 --> 04:26.440
I was gonna pay, there was
just so much chaos in there.

04:26.520 --> 04:30.320
Too bad you forgot,
now you'll have to come with me.

04:35.280 --> 04:36.520
[woman over radio]
Reception.

04:36.600 --> 04:39.240
[Mette] Hello, could you please put me
through to Human Resources at the PST?

04:39.320 --> 04:42.080
- One moment.
- Hi, Sturle.

04:42.160 --> 04:43.880
- [Sturle]  Hi.
- [Mette] Hi.

04:43.960 --> 04:48.600
That guy we used to call The Bat,
is he still with the Service?

04:48.680 --> 04:51.600
Yes. I believe he works in the archives.

04:51.680 --> 04:52.800
Okay.

04:57.320 --> 04:58.640
[grunts]

04:58.720 --> 05:01.680
Okay, thank you, Sturle.

05:01.760 --> 05:02.920
[in English] Yes.

05:03.920 --> 05:05.440
[sighs]

05:13.520 --> 05:15.880
[in Norwegian]
So this is where your buddy lives.

05:15.960 --> 05:20.240
[in English] Ah, it's more
like a temporary residence.

05:20.320 --> 05:22.120
[guard in Norwegian]
I'll take your jacket.

05:27.640 --> 05:30.640
