- You seem to have beeped.

05:33.640 --> 05:35.560
[wand beeping]

05:35.640 --> 05:36.920
Okay.

05:37.000 --> 05:38.200
[beeping]

05:38.280 --> 05:39.960
I have a piercing down there.

05:40.040 --> 05:43.600
That's something I'll have to check,
unfortunately.

05:47.080 --> 05:48.560
[Aadne clears throat]

05:48.640 --> 05:50.560
