08:37.320 --> 08:38.920
Well...

08:39.000 --> 08:41.120
You're always hanging out
with those asylum people.

08:41.200 --> 08:43.560
Why don't you stay here.
Party with the guys?

08:43.640 --> 08:46.760
Sounds nice,
but I really have to go.

08:46.840 --> 08:48.120
It's kind of a special occasion tonight.

08:48.200 --> 08:50.960
- And what's so special?
- Well,

08:51.040 --> 08:54.720
I think they might've
organized something up there

08:54.800 --> 08:56.880
since it's my birthday.

08:56.960 --> 08:58.840
It's your birthday?
Why haven't you said anything?

08:58.920 --> 09:00.320
It's your birthday today?

09:00.400 --> 09:02.160
- [Roar] Shit! Congratulations.
- [Torgeir] Congratulations.

09:02.240 --> 09:05.240
- Thanks, thanks.
- [whistles] Cindy!

09:05.320 --> 09:07.600
- It is Jan's turn.
- No, no.

09:07.680 --> 09:09.400
- [Roar] It is.
- Stop it.

09:09.480 --> 09:11.320
[men laugh]

09:13.840 --> 09:16.000
Come on.

09:16.080 --> 09:17.640
Put on some music!

09:17.720 --> 09:19.880
[Stagedolls'
"Love Don't Bother Me" playing]

09:19.960 --> 09:22.640
[Jan]
You guys!

09:22.720 --> 09:25.200
Maybe I'll stay a bit longer after all.

09:29.360 --> 09:31.480
[cheering]

09:31.560 --> 09:33.120
