09:54.400 --> 09:57.640
Oh, that? Just an innocent
boys' game on my birthday.

09:57.720 --> 10:01.520
Stop it. I heard what you said
to that poor girl.

10:01.600 --> 10:04.400
Oh, but that's just our tone

10:04.480 --> 10:07.480
here at the Flamingo,
a kind of tribal language.

10:07.560 --> 10:10.680
Tribal language? Fuck that.

10:10.760 --> 10:12.280
You--
Wait, Randi, I'm coming.

10:12.360 --> 10:15.680
No! You can just forget it.

10:15.760 --> 10:19.680
