10:35.200 --> 10:39.000
[all singing "Happy Birthday" in English]

10:42.200 --> 10:44.600
[in Norwegian]
He isn't coming. Sit down!

10:44.680 --> 10:46.360
I need some of your herb.

10:46.440 --> 10:49.360
- What's up? I thought you quit.
- You were wrong.

10:49.440 --> 10:50.840
But I have promised Jan not to--

10:50.920 --> 10:53.080
Give me some right away,

10:53.160 --> 10:54.800
or I'll kick that black ass of yours

10:54.880 --> 10:57.240
so fucking far out of this country that...

10:57.320 --> 11:00.360
[piano playing "Happy Birthday"]

11:00.440 --> 11:03.480
Okay, okay.
One hundred percent.

11:05.880 --> 11:08.400
[piano keys thunk]

11:11.000 --> 11:12.320
[door slams]

11:40.240 --> 11:41.960
[in English]
That's gotta be our guy.

11:43.880 --> 11:45.480
Give me your badge.

11:45.560 --> 11:47.080
Huh?

11:47.160 --> 11:48.920
Give me your badge.

11:56.240 --> 11:57.760
Psst.

11:59.960 --> 12:05.120
[in Norwegian] I have a customer now.
You have to order at the desk.

12:05.200 --> 12:08.200
[in English]
Get lost, honey. And don't come back.

12:21.960 --> 12:23.720
[gasps]

12:23.800 --> 12:25.960
