My nipples are very sensitive.

13:15.160 --> 13:15.960
Mm-hmm.

13:16.520 --> 13:18.840
[screams]

13:29.600 --> 13:31.080
[Torgeir snoring]

13:37.840 --> 13:39.520
[groans]

13:42.480 --> 13:44.160
[in Norwegian]
Momma?

13:44.240 --> 13:46.400
Momma?

13:46.480 --> 13:49.280
Shut up. You're sleep-talking
about Mom again.

13:49.360 --> 13:54.200
[Wenche] Aw, look at my boys.

13:56.760 --> 14:00.040
All grown up!

14:04.080 --> 14:06.920
What the fuck are you doing here?

14:07.000 --> 14:11.320
I stopped by at the farm.
The neighbor said I'd find you here.

14:12.520 --> 14:15.200
My meaning was,
what the fuck are you doing in Norway?

14:15.280 --> 14:16.800
Calm down. My God.

14:16.880 --> 14:18.640
- It is nice to see you.
- Yes, yes.

14:18.720 --> 14:21.960
I am sorry that I haven't gotten
around to visiting you sooner.

14:22.040 --> 14:26.120
- I apologize.
- Relax, Mom. You are here now.

14:26.200 --> 14:27.400
[Wenche]
My big, strong boy--

14:27.480 --> 14:31.400
Would've been even nicer if it didn't take
10 years between each visit.

14:45.640 --> 14:47.520
Do you like chai lattes?

14:48.040 --> 14:50.000
Who doesn't.

14:52.320 --> 14:55.280
Ready for the first day
of the rest of your life, my friend?

14:55.360 --> 14:56.600
[in English] You betcha.

15:01.160 --> 15:04.480
[in Norwegian] So when that cult stuff is
suddenly not so groovy anymore,

15:04.560 --> 15:07.280
