for her, is that it?

15:07.360 --> 15:11.160
Let loose, Torgeir.
Do like the rappers say.

15:11.240 --> 15:13.080
[in English]
"Chillax, motherfucker."

15:13.160 --> 15:15.240
[in Norwegian] Don't believe
those rappers ever met our mom.

15:15.320 --> 15:17.600
- [door opens]
- [Wenche laughing]

15:17.680 --> 15:20.640
Here's someone you have to meet.

15:20.720 --> 15:24.120
Stanley, the new rock in my life.

15:25.600 --> 15:27.040
[Stanley]
Hi.

15:27.120 --> 15:30.520
Shit. I didn't know
you were such big shots.

15:30.600 --> 15:33.360
Pow! Pow!

15:33.440 --> 15:35.360
