15:48.480 --> 15:51.240
[in Norwegian]
This must be Roar.

15:51.320 --> 15:55.000
- That's correct.
- Hi. The funny one.

15:55.080 --> 15:56.880
[Roar]
Exactly.

15:56.960 --> 15:59.240
Belinda! Could we have
some champagne for our guests.

15:59.320 --> 16:01.600
Champagne?
Let's slow down a little.

16:01.680 --> 16:03.360
Stop it.

16:03.440 --> 16:06.800
- Take a cava, at least.
- [Wenche] They've never changed.

16:06.880 --> 16:09.680
Roar so generous

16:09.760 --> 16:12.280
and Torgeir more restrained.

16:12.360 --> 16:13.800
[Wench and Stanley laugh]

16:13.880 --> 16:16.640
Plus and... minus.

16:16.720 --> 16:18.920
- [Stanley laughs]
- [Wenche] Yeah.

16:21.080 --> 16:23.840
I bought you some stuff.

16:23.920 --> 16:25.400
