16:25.480 --> 16:28.800
And the world's best  pata negra.

16:28.960 --> 16:34.080
This is better service than
in Norwegian prisons, I promise you.

16:34.160 --> 16:37.120
Can I take a shower?

16:37.200 --> 16:39.880
Yeah, sure.

16:47.720 --> 16:50.200
[in English]
Enjoying your freedom, Tommy boy?

16:50.280 --> 16:53.720
I wish we could leave our doors
open like that in Brooklyn.

16:53.800 --> 16:56.640
That orange you tried to sell us,

16:56.720 --> 16:59.040
turned out to be a lemon.

16:59.120 --> 17:03.400
[in Norwegian]
Johnny, don't be gangsterish about that.

17:03.480 --> 17:07.120
I made an honest attempt to help you.
Really. Cross my heart.

17:07.200 --> 17:10.040
[in English] Cross your heart
and hope to die, Tommy boy?

17:10.120 --> 17:11.600
Huh?

17:12.720 --> 17:14.760
[Zlatan in Norwegian] Who the fuck are you
to think you can come in here

17:14.840 --> 17:17.600
- and mess with my friend?
- [Thomas] Easy now, easy boys.

17:17.680 --> 17:19.560
[in English]
You muscle up on your first day out?

17:19.640 --> 17:22.760
[in Norwegian] Nobody has muscled up
anything. This is my New Path mentor.

17:22.840 --> 17:25.440
He's helping me get back on track.

17:25.520 --> 17:28.040
[in English] I'm sure Dirty Harry
will put you on the right path.

17:29.280 --> 17:30.800
[Thomas in Norwegian]
Listen, guys.

17:30.880 --> 17:35.200
In prison, we had these classes called
Coping with Conflict.

17:35.280 --> 17:37.920
