what they had on the heart.

17:42.880 --> 17:45.160
[in Norwegian] Sounds like a good idea.
Let's do that!

17:48.720 --> 17:50.240
[slurping]

17:54.160 --> 17:56.920
[in English] Okay, well.

17:57.000 --> 18:01.960
[in Norwegian] Here's the case.
These guys here, they sped up my release.

18:02.040 --> 18:05.800
In return, they expect some information.

18:05.880 --> 18:09.520
What kind of information
are we talking about?

18:09.600 --> 18:13.160
Who's behind the Bieber Heist.

18:13.240 --> 18:15.440
Why didn't you just say so?

18:15.520 --> 18:17.840
[in English]
I can find out those things.

18:17.920 --> 18:20.000
[in Norwegian]
I am straight now,

18:20.080 --> 18:23.880
but I did five years
for armed robbery before that.

18:23.960 --> 18:26.440
But...

18:26.520 --> 18:27.920
Problem is, I'm pretty lazy.

18:28.000 --> 18:30.880
I need strong incentives
to get my ass in gear.

18:30.960 --> 18:34.360
- If you understand my drift.
- [chuckles]

18:34.440 --> 18:36.400
[in English]
Yeah.

18:36.480 --> 18:40.240
Yeah, well, for the right information,

18:40.320 --> 18:42.880
we got a hundred thousand
incentives for you.

18:50.840 --> 18:52.720
[in Norwegian]
You'll hear from us.

18:56.320 --> 19:00.080
[band playing "Girl in Oslo"]

19:31.520 --> 19:35.480
[in Norwegian] Oh! God!
Can someone turn that heat down!

19:35.560 --> 19:38.480
Torry! Torry boy!

19:38.560 --> 19:39.920
Turn down the heat.

19:40.000 --> 19:42.600
[Torgeir]
Sorry, no. And my name is Torgeir.

19:46.960 --> 19:50.920
Listen, boy.
Your mother's almost got heat shock.

19:51.000 --> 19:52.640
It's like a fucking sauna in here.

19:52.720 --> 19:55.600
